<li><a href="https://github.com/hillu/go-yara" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">go-yara <ExternalLinkIcon/></a><a href="https://github.com/plusvic/yara" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">-YARA<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>的 Go Bindings ，“恶意软件研究人员（和其他所有人）的模式匹配瑞士刀”。</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/dwin/goArgonPass" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">goArgonPass<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> - Argon2 密码哈希和验证旨在与现有的 Python 和 PHP 实现兼容。</li>
